purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values represents diuretic medications.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who are on diuretic medications.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Medication category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes RxNorm codes to represent single and multi-ingredient drugs in oral and injectable dose forms.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
